    <item>
      <title>英国失业率意外下降 表明经济强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/uk-unemployment-dips-unexpectedly-but-growth-in-wages-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国失业率在企业加大招聘力度后意外下降，这表明英国经济潜在实力增强，但这给英国央行降低利率的举措带来困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/uk-unemployment-dips-unexpectedly-but-growth-in-wages-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 06:11:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
